fwprop.note:
Start Action for Command (11,4) to insert one or more time-based activites (TBAs) in the time-based schedule (TBS). 
The command carries the sub-schedule identifier and, for each activity, its release time, its group identifier and the command.

fwprop.entryDesc:
Set action outcome to 'failure'
with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_SS and
load sub-schedule identifier in verFailData

fwprop.note:
This procedure generates a (1,4) report for each TBA it rejects. The (1,4) reports are generated by the
Command Verification Failure Procedure. The start action is declared successful as long as at least one TBA is accepted.
Sub-schedule identifier is illegal if it is outside: 1...SCD_N_SUB_TBS

fwprop.entryDesc:
Set i equal to 1 and
load 1 in verFailData

Load group identifier in verFailData and
Run Command Verification Failure Procedure to
generate (1,4) report with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_G

fwprop.note:
Group identifier is illegal if it is outside: 1...SCD_N_GROUP
or if its InUse flag is set to FALSE

fwprop.entryDesc:
Load coarse part of release time in verFailData and
Run Command Verification Failure Procedure to
generate (1,4) report with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_RT

fwprop.note: Release time is illegal if it is less than (current time + time margin)

fwprop.entryDesc:
Load destination in verFailData and
Run Command Verification Failure Procedure to
generate (1,4) report with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_DS

Run Verifucation Failure Procedure to generate 
(1,4) report with failure code VER_FULL_TBS

Use the make operation of the InFactory to create an
InCommand encapsulating the command embedded in the TBA

Run Verifucation Failure Procedure to generate
(1,4) report with failure code VER_SCD_CRFAIL

fwprop.note:
This indicates that either there are no resources to create
the new InCommand or the [type,subtype,discriminant] of the
command are illegal

fwprop.entryDesc:
Increment i and
load i in verFailData

Set action outcome to 'failure'
with failure code VER_SCD_ST_FD

fwprop.guardDesc:
Destination of command embedded 
in TBA is not the host application

The i-th TBA was not the last 
TBA in the command

All TBAs in te command
have been rejected
